| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2673 — Recovery Inhibition (chaos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ff9e5177-d50c-5dba-94cc-8f3ecc88d8ab"
